[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 0.0,
    "text": "(Upbeat music) - Don't mind me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.57,
    "text": "Just freaking out a little bit here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.58,
    "endTime": 5.413,
    "text": "Hi guys, it's Matt. (orchestral music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.413,
    "endTime": 7.16,
    "text": "- Welcome back to my kitchen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.16,
    "endTime": 9.77,
    "text": "Here on Tasty we've made tons of great recipes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.77,
    "endTime": 11.58,
    "text": "on how to make your own fast food at home,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.58,
    "endTime": 14.11,
    "text": "but there is one thing we've never been able to capture"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.11,
    "endTime": 17.22,
    "text": "and that is the speed and convenience of fast food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.22,
    "endTime": 19.529,
    "text": "So today, in order to put that to the test,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.53,
    "endTime": 21.51,
    "text": "I'm going to attempt to make one of my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.51,
    "endTime": 23.92,
    "text": "favorite fast food burgers, the Big Mac,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.92,
    "endTime": 25.67,
    "text": "in the same amount of time it takes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.67,
    "endTime": 27.51,
    "text": "to have one delivered to my house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.51,
    "endTime": 28.608,
    "text": "We'll see how this goes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.608,
    "endTime": 30.38,
    "text": "(dramatic orchestral music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.38,
    "endTime": 32.519,
    "text": "This is the most nervous I've been for a video,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.52,
    "endTime": 34.89,
    "text": "because as soon as I start, I cannot stop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.89,
    "endTime": 36.24,
    "text": "Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.24,
    "endTime": 38.480000000000004,
    "text": "Confirming order, preparing your order."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.48,
    "endTime": 39.696,
    "text": "We are unable to authorize your card."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.697,
    "endTime": 40.53,
    "text": "(beep)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.53,
    "endTime": 41.56,
    "text": "Okay, McDonald's is preparing my order."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.56,
    "endTime": 43.760000000000005,
    "text": "First thing I'm gonna start with is my special sauce."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.76,
    "endTime": 45.04,
    "text": "I am going to add,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.04,
    "endTime": 46.29,
    "text": "mayonnaise,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.29,
    "endTime": 48.089,
    "text": "my pickle,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.09,
    "endTime": 49.440000000000005,
    "text": "a bit of mustard,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.44,
    "endTime": 51.339,
    "text": "and then onion powder,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.34,
    "endTime": 52.470000000000006,
    "text": "garlic powder,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.47,
    "endTime": 53.46,
    "text": "paprika,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.46,
    "endTime": 54.95,
    "text": "and finally, white pepper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.95,
    "endTime": 56.1,
    "text": "This bowl is way to small."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.1,
    "endTime": 56.933,
    "text": "You know what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.933,
    "endTime": 58.173,
    "text": "Just gonna mix it anyways."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 61.53,
    "text": "They have assigned a driver."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.53,
    "endTime": 62.79,
    "text": "I am so screwed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.79,
    "endTime": 64.459,
    "text": "Oh my freaking god."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.459,
    "endTime": 66.24000000000001,
    "text": "Okay, special sauce is done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.24,
    "endTime": 69.86,
    "text": "Going to quickly dice up my onion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.86,
    "endTime": 71.98,
    "text": "Got my iceberg lettuce."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.98,
    "endTime": 73.9,
    "text": "I'm only gonna use a quarter of a head for this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.9,
    "endTime": 75.39,
    "text": "And I'm just gonna shred this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.39,
    "endTime": 77.82000000000001,
    "text": "Finally, I just want to prep my bun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.82,
    "endTime": 79.13,
    "text": "Because it has that middle bun,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.13,
    "endTime": 82.312,
    "text": "I just want to trim one of the bottom pieces to use for it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.67,
    "endTime": 86.24,
    "text": "Okay, John has arrived."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.24,
    "endTime": 87.417,
    "text": "I gotta get the burner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.417,
    "endTime": 88.48,
    "text": "Where's the burner?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.48,
    "endTime": 89.9,
    "text": "Prep my burner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.9,
    "endTime": 91.51,
    "text": "As my burner is heating up,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.51,
    "endTime": 93.55000000000001,
    "text": "I'm going to butter my buns."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.55,
    "endTime": 95.16,
    "text": "And I'm just using sesame buns for this,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.16,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "but you can really use whatever buns you want."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 99.81,
    "text": "Just let these get nice and toasty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.81,
    "endTime": 100.643,
    "text": "Everette, you're looking at me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.643,
    "endTime": 101.476,
    "text": "why you looking at me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.476,
    "endTime": 102.309,
    "text": "Is John on his way?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.61,
    "endTime": 106.34,
    "text": "Okay, perfect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.34,
    "endTime": 109.52000000000001,
    "text": "Buns are almost done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.52,
    "endTime": 110.96,
    "text": "Set those to the side."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.96,
    "endTime": 113.339,
    "text": "Alright, so for my patties I'm keeping it nice and simple."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.34,
    "endTime": 116.25,
    "text": "I'm just doing 80/20 lean to fat content."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.25,
    "endTime": 117.481,
    "text": "So I'm gonna put my beef down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.481,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "(meat sizzling)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 121.28,
    "text": "And I'm just gonna smash."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.61,
    "endTime": 126.01,
    "text": "Let's do salt on top."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.01,
    "endTime": 127.19000000000001,
    "text": "Cracked pepper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.19,
    "endTime": 128.472,
    "text": "Everette, how am I doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.87,
    "endTime": 131.03900000000002,
    "text": "He's still at McDonalds?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.039,
    "endTime": 133.58999999999997,
    "text": "I could win this, I actually feel good about this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.59,
    "endTime": 134.423,
    "text": "Looks good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.423,
    "endTime": 136.46,
    "text": "And I'm going to flip."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.46,
    "endTime": 138.04000000000002,
    "text": "Oh perfect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.04,
    "endTime": 139.14,
    "text": "Perfect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.14,
    "endTime": 140.79,
    "text": "You can see that it's a nice golden brown."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.79,
    "endTime": 143.452,
    "text": "I'm just gonna top one slice with my cheese."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.452,
    "endTime": 145.593,
    "text": "I'd say that's probably good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.563,
    "endTime": 149.28,
    "text": "Wobash and wobash."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.28,
    "endTime": 151.15,
    "text": "Alrighty, so I think I'm in the clear at this point,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.15,
    "endTime": 152.56,
    "text": "but before I jinx myself,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.56,
    "endTime": 155.43,
    "text": "I'm going to start with my bottom bun,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.43,
    "endTime": 157.01000000000002,
    "text": "add some lettuce,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.01,
    "endTime": 158.06,
    "text": "some onion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.9,
    "endTime": 162.33,
    "text": "couple little dill pickles"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.33,
    "endTime": 163.46,
    "text": "got my middle bun,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.46,
    "endTime": 165.72,
    "text": "some of that special sauce, secret sauce."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.72,
    "endTime": 167.75,
    "text": "Is it secret or special sauce?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.75,
    "endTime": 170.4,
    "text": "Top with a little bit more lettuce,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.4,
    "endTime": 171.76000000000002,
    "text": "little bit more onion,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.76,
    "endTime": 174.739,
    "text": "top with my final piece of meat,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.74,
    "endTime": 176.42000000000002,
    "text": "add two more pickles,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.42,
    "endTime": 178.29,
    "text": "special sauce on my top bun,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.29,
    "endTime": 179.6,
    "text": "and wobash."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.6,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "Boom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 181.78,
    "text": "That is a homemade Big Mac."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.78,
    "endTime": 182.693,
    "text": "Where's John at?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.877,
    "endTime": 185.28,
    "text": "Yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.28,
    "endTime": 186.629,
    "text": "I think I did that in under fifteen minutes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.629,
    "endTime": 187.462,
    "text": "(beep)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.462,
    "endTime": 188.295,
    "text": "I'm gonna -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.595,
    "endTime": 192.799,
    "text": "(meat sizzling)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.799,
    "endTime": 193.632,
    "text": "(clock ticking)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.632,
    "endTime": 196.08100000000002,
    "text": "We've got two Big Macs in the time it takes to order one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.081,
    "endTime": 196.914,
    "text": "(clock ticking)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.914,
    "endTime": 199.95,
    "text": "(Dramatic orchestral music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.95,
    "endTime": 200.789,
    "text": "So right off the bat,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.789,
    "endTime": 202.339,
    "text": "mine looks pretty good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.34,
    "endTime": 204.87,
    "text": "It's got a lot of vertical height to it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.87,
    "endTime": 206.88,
    "text": "Feels like a lot more burger,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.88,
    "endTime": 209.26,
    "text": "and honestly it looks like a good comparison"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.26,
    "endTime": 211.17,
    "text": "to the delivery one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.17,
    "endTime": 212.70899999999997,
    "text": "So the moment of truth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.71,
    "endTime": 215.28300000000002,
    "text": "It's time to try my burgers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.01,
    "endTime": 217.843,
    "text": "It's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.843,
    "endTime": 218.676,
    "text": "It's a Big Mac."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.676,
    "endTime": 220.01,
    "text": "It's exactly what you'd expect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.01,
    "endTime": 220.843,
    "text": "Consistent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.843,
    "endTime": 221.84,
    "text": "You got he balance of the sauce,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.84,
    "endTime": 222.673,
    "text": "and the lettuce, and the onions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.673,
    "endTime": 223.506,
    "text": "and the pickle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.506,
    "endTime": 225.3,
    "text": "So let's give the homemade a try."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.3,
    "endTime": 226.27,
    "text": "The homemade one is awesome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.27,
    "endTime": 227.5,
    "text": "It's got the char from the griddle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.5,
    "endTime": 229.37,
    "text": "I feel like McDonald's burgers don't always get that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.37,
    "endTime": 231.31,
    "text": "nice, sorta browning on them that you'd like."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.31,
    "endTime": 232.42000000000002,
    "text": "Got the crunchy lettuce,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.42,
    "endTime": 233.92899999999997,
    "text": "you got the fluffy bun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.93,
    "endTime": 236.82,
    "text": "This is a great homemade interpretation of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.82,
    "endTime": 239.147,
    "text": "Any body want the one I took a bite out of?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.147,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "Everette?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.0,
    "endTime": 241.43,
    "text": "And there you have it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.43,
    "endTime": 243.5,
    "text": "In a race against my delivery,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.5,
    "endTime": 246.09,
    "text": "I was able to make two Big Macs in the time it takes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.09,
    "endTime": 247.48,
    "text": "to make and deliver one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.48,
    "endTime": 248.5,
    "text": "Let me know what you guys think"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.5,
    "endTime": 250.46,
    "text": "in the comments section below."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.46,
    "endTime": 251.87,
    "text": "If you guys have any other ideas,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.87,
    "endTime": 253.82,
    "text": "or any other delivery options you want us to try,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.82,
    "endTime": 255.43,
    "text": "also let me know in the comments below."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.43,
    "endTime": 257.03000000000003,
    "text": "And until then, take care."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.029,
    "endTime": 258.712,
    "text": "Oh yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.713,
    "endTime": 262.213,
    "text": "(joyful orchestral music)"
  }
]